{"tid":134231,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"水點蒸發變做白雪？","createTime":"2017-02-25T10:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T11:17:27.000Z","uid":26169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae38deb7e8950ff109cc1a5c29f7b39a026e9b2","tid":134231,"uid":26169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"雲是地球上龐大的水循環的有形的結果。太陽照在地球的表面，水蒸發形成水蒸氣，一旦水汽過飽和，水分子就會聚集在空氣中的微塵（凝結核）周圍，由此產生的水滴或冰晶將陽光散射到各個方向，這就產生了雲的外觀。因為雲反射和散射所有波段的電磁波，所以雲的顏色成灰度色，雲層比較薄時成白色，但是當它們變得太厚或濃密而使得陽光不能通過的話，它們可以看起來是灰色或黑色的。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/云\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%BA%91&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=41fa702c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/云</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花瓣飄落下游生根"},{"pid":"5e90666fc6a4bc2b0c3859e24f81d7dde5674f6e","tid":134231,"uid":26169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"白雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fef7bc27d2c319f70a4c2635488db20b04690c","tid":134231,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"遇怪魔我點即刻變大個"},{"pid":"f90388997b1b7d15822d01d4707e5c8ee43e1a8b","tid":134231,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"花瓣飄落下游生根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9e418a481370c050b76d153319b0379316e4e2","tid":134231,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"人地問你 你又問返人？"},{"pid":"7bbd5b96af0fecf2369e9dd88e01463aed6bec49","tid":134231,"uid":84786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遇怪魔我點即刻變大個</blockquote><br />\n咬手指或者整個傷口"},{"pid":"b162